Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Diplomacy and the Star Wars defence program
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjvtz
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 May 1996
The diplomacies of Wilson and Roosevelt, Ronald Reagan's Star Wars defence programme, and the American response to international elections, as detailed by Alistair Cooke.